{"id":161307,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/《苹果日报》称香港汽车被安装了窃听器/","date":"2011-06-15T07:32:12Z","modified":"2011-06-15T07:32:12Z","title":"《苹果日报》称香港汽车被安装了窃听器","content":"<p>《苹果日报》报导（原文已删除，快照），所有持中港牌车辆，均被加装了具有窃听功能的电子仪器。 该窃听仪器植入在“检验检疫车载卡”，是内地当局2007年7月开始为所有中港车免费安装，计划由深圳检验检疫局执行。“车载卡”外形及大小与电子手帐相若，以双面胶纸牢牢黏在车厢内的车头玻璃上，仪器背部螺丝位更盖上保护贴，防止有人私下拆开仪器。城市大学电子工程学系副教授郑利明检查了该设备，证实具有窃听功能，他声称其接收范围达到方圆20公里。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/15dda140/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E3%80%8A%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5%E3%80%8B%E7%A7%B0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E8%A2%AB%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BA%86%E7%AA%83%E5%90%AC%E5%99%A8&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F06%2F14%2F0537226%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E3%80%8A%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5%E3%80%8B%E7%A7%B0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E8%A2%AB%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BA%86%E7%AA%83%E5%90%AC%E5%99%A8&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F06%2F14%2F0537226%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/104471965069/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/15dda140/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/104471965069/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/15dda140/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=xREnR6sMZNI:QoqIsqLMoog:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=xREnR6sMZNI:QoqIsqLMoog:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.f